<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WanderWithUs</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e") no-repeat center/cover;
            height: 60vh;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        nav {
            background: #4a90e2;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .blog-post {
            background: white;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .blog-post img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #4a90e2;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            background: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #357ABD;
        }

        .more-content {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #333;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Wander With Us</h1>
    <p>Exploring the world one place at a time ✈️</p>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Destinations</a>
    <a href="#">Travel Tips</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

    <!-- 🌄 Mountains -->
    <div class="blog-post">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501785888041-af3ef285b470">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Trip to the Mountains</h2>
            <p>I explored beautiful mountain landscapes and peaceful surroundings.</p>

            <div class="more-content">
                <p>My trip to the mountains was one of the most peaceful experiences of my life. Surrounded by tall peaks and fresh air, it felt magical.</p>
                <p>I enjoyed sunrise views, trekking, and local food. The calm environment helped me relax and reconnect with nature.</p>
                <p>This journey taught me the importance of taking breaks and enjoying simple moments.</p>
            </div>

            <span class="btn" onclick="toggleContent(this)">Read More</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 🌊 Beach -->
    <div class="blog-post">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493558103817-58b2924bce98">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Relaxing at the Beach</h2>
            <p>The sound of waves and sunsets made this trip unforgettable.</p>

            <div class="more-content">
                <p>The beach was calm and refreshing. Walking on the sand and watching sunsets was amazing.</p>
                <p>I tried water activities and enjoyed seafood. The peaceful vibe made it a perfect escape.</p>
                <p>This trip helped me relax and recharge completely.</p>
            </div>

            <span class="btn" onclick="toggleContent(this)">Read More</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 🌆 City -->
    <div class="blog-post">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505761671935-60b3a7427bad">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>City Adventures</h2>
            <p>Exploring the vibrant city life was full of excitement.</p>

            <div class="more-content">
                <p>The city was full of energy, lights, and activity. I visited markets and tourist spots.</p>
                <p>Street food and nightlife were highlights of the trip. Every place had something unique.</p>
                <p>This experience showed me how dynamic and fun city life can be.</p>
            </div>

            <span class="btn" onclick="toggleContent(this)">Read More</span>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 WanderWithUs | Travel Blog</p>
</footer>

<script>
function toggleContent(button) {
    const content = button.previousElementSibling;

    if (content.style.display === "block") {
        content.style.display = "none";
        button.textContent = "Read More";
    } else {
        content.style.display = "block";
        button.textContent = "Show Less";
    }
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
